info.author: vrbulatov
info.description:
1. Uninstall GDS
2. unpack GDS setup file (UPX.exe -d GoogleDestopSearchSetup.exe )
3. Patch setup file ( ChangeGDSSetup -c GoogleDestopSearchSetup.exe abap=txt 
c=txt cs=txt java=txt txt=txt dot=doc doc=doc zip=zip rar=zip ). For detail see 
( ChangeGDSSetup -v GoogleDestopSearchSetup.exe ) -- view current option
